title: CDH5 Salt Formula
description: Salt formula for installing components of CDH5
root_path: cdh5
components:
  - title: NameNode
    description: Hadoop NameNode component of CDH5
    sls_path: cdh5.hadoop.namenode
  - title: DataNode
